<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_f2953ce093b7.aspx"><b>鱼藻</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonf2953ce093b7">
<p>鱼在在藻，有颁其首。王在在镐，岂乐饮酒。</p>
<p>鱼在在藻，有莘其尾。王在在镐，饮酒乐岂。</p>
<p>鱼在在藻，依于其蒲。王在在镐，有那其居。</p>
</div>
</div>
